<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-900 min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center p-4">

    <div class="bg-slate-800 w-full max-w-md rounded-2xl shadow-2xl border border-slate-700 p-8 text-center">
        
        <div class="mb-6">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-amber-500/10 text-amber-400 mb-3 ring-8 ring-amber-500/5">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-mobile-screen-button text-xl"></i>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight">Configurar MFA</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm mt-1">Asociación de Autenticación Multifactor obligatoria</p>
        </div>

        <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm mb-6">
            Escanea el siguiente código QR con la aplicación <strong>Google Authenticator</strong> en tu celular para activar tu segundo factor de seguridad.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-white p-4 inline-block rounded-xl shadow-inner mb-6">
            <img src="<%= qrCodeUrl %>" alt="Código QR MFA" class="w-48 h-48 mx-auto">
        </div>

        <div class="mb-6 text-left">
            <label class="block text-xs font-medium text-slate-400 mb-1">¿No puedes escanearlo? Clave manual:</label>
            <div class="bg-slate-900 px-3 py-2 rounded border border-slate-700 text-xs font-mono text-amber-400 break-all select-all">
                <%= secret %>
            </div>
        </div>

        <a href="/login" 
            class="w-full inline-flex justify-center py-3 px-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm text-sm font-semibold text-white bg-amber-600 hover:bg-amber-500 transition-all duration-150">
            Ya lo escaneé, ir al Login
        </a>

    </div>

</body>
</html>